---
layout: base.njk
title: 首页
description: 小说资料、学习经验、折腾记录和随手文章，都放在这里。
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">个人文章库</p>
    <h1>写小说，也写生活；<br>写经验，也写乱七八糟的想法。</h1>
    <p class="hero-text">这里不是单一主题博客，而是一个长期积累的个人文章库。仙逆资料、学习经验、建站折腾、随手随笔，都可以放在这里。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href="/posts/">查看全部文章</a>
      <a class="button ghost" href="/search/">搜索内容</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="hero-card">
    <div><span class="stat">{{ collections.posts.length }}</span><span>篇文章</span></div>
    <div><span class="stat">{{ collections.all | tagList | length }}</span><span>个标签</span></div>
    <div><span class="stat">∞</span><span>持续更新</span></div>
  </aside>
</section>

<section class="section-head">
  <h2>最新文章</h2>
  <a href="/posts/">查看全部</a>
</section>

<section class="post-grid">
{% for post in collections.posts | limit(6) %}
  <a class="post-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
    <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
    <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    <span>阅读全文 →</span>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="feature-row">
  <div class="feature"><b>小说资料</b><span>人物、境界、剧情节点，随时补充。</span></div>
  <div class="feature"><b>学习经验</b><span>方法、复盘、成长记录，留给以后回看。</span></div>
  <div class="feature"><b>折腾笔记</b><span>建站、工具、技术试验，不再丢三落四。</span></div>
</section>
